OL,3,CFlagship welfare reform plans to be
OL,4,Cintroduced in Parliament
OL,6,FMinisters also want to cut the
OL,7,Fsickness related element of universal
OL,8,Fcredit (UC), and delay access to it,
OL,9,Fso only those aged 22 and over can
OL,10,Fclaim it.
OL,12,FThe package of reforms is aimed at
OL,13,Fencouraging more people off sickness
OL,14,Fbenefits and into work, and the
OL,15,FGovernment hopes it can save up to #5
OL,16,Fbillion a year by doing so.
