OL,3,CFlagship welfare reform plans to be
OL,4,Cintroduced in Parliament
OL,6,FBut ministers are likely to face a
OL,7,FCommons stand-off with backbench
OL,8,FLabour MPs over their plans, with
OL,9,Fdozens of them last month saying the
OL,10,Fproposals were "impossible to support".
OL,12,FThe Bill is set to be introduced as
OL,13,Fthe latest benefits data has shown
OL,14,Fthat more than 3.7 million people in
OL,15,FEngland and Wales are claiming Pip,
OL,16,Fwith teenagers and young adults making
OL,17,Fup a growing proportion.
