OL,3,CFlagship welfare reform plans to be
OL,4,Cintroduced in Parliament
OL,6,FThe latest data, published by the
OL,7,FDepartment for Work and Pensions on
OL,8,FTuesday, showed there were a record
OL,9,F3.74 million people in England and
OL,10,FWales claiming Pip as of April this
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FThe figure is up from 3.69 million in
OL,14,FJanuary and a jump of 200,000 from
OL,15,F3.54 million a year earlier.
OL,17,FData for Pip claimants begins in
OL,18,FJanuary 2019, when the number stood at
OL,19,F2.05 million.
