OL,3,CFlagship welfare reform plans to be
OL,4,Cintroduced in Parliament
OL,6,FPip is a benefit aimed at helping with
OL,7,Fextra living costs if someone has a
OL,8,Flong-term physical or mental health
OL,9,Fcondition or disability and difficulty
OL,10,Fdoing certain everyday tasks or
OL,11,Fgetting around because of their
OL,12,Fcondition.
OL,14,FTeenagers and young adults account for
OL,15,Fa growing proportion of those getting
OL,16,FPip.
OL,18,FSome 16.5% of claimants in April this
OL,19,Fyear were aged 16-19, up from 14.6% in
OL,20,FApril 2019.
