OL,3,CFlagship welfare reform plans to be
OL,4,Cintroduced in Parliament
OL,6,FThe 30-44 age group has similarly
OL,7,Fgrown, while the number of 45-59 year-
OL,8,Folds has fallen.
OL,10,FThe figure for 60-74 year-olds has
OL,11,Frisen slightly over this period, from
OL,12,F29.3% to 30.8%.
OL,14,FIt was reported in recent days that
OL,15,FWork and Pensions Secretary Liz
OL,16,FKendall has agreed to include "non-
OL,17,Fnegotiable" protections in the Bill,
OL,18,Fincluding a guarantee that those who
OL,19,Fno longer qualify for Pip will still
OL,20,Freceive the payments for 13 weeks,
OL,21,Frather than just four weeks.
