OL,3,CFlagship welfare reform plans to be
OL,4,Cintroduced in Parliament
OL,6,FThe concession is seen as a move to
OL,7,Favert a rebellion by Labour MPs
OL,8,Fopposed to the overall reforms, but
OL,9,Fhave been described as "not very much
OL,10,Freally" by one such parliamentarian.
OL,12,FDowning Street insisted it was
OL,13,F"crucial to say we are committed to
OL,14,Fthe reforms that we've set out".
OL,16,FA No 10 spokesman said: "You've heard
OL,17,Fthat from the Prime Minister, the
OL,18,FChancellor, the Work and Pensions
OL,19,FSecretary, on the principles behind
OL,20,Fthis and the urgent need for this.
