OL,3,CFlagship welfare reform plans to be
OL,4,Cintroduced in Parliament
OL,6,FPip will remain "an important non-
OL,7,Fmeans-tested benefit for disabled
OL,8,Fpeople and people with long-term
OL,9,Fhealth conditions, regardless of
OL,10,Fwhether they are in or out of work",
OL,11,Fhe said, but added the Government
OL,12,Fwould build a "system that is fairer"
OL,13,Fthrough its reforms.
OL,15,FIt is thought the restrictions on Pip
OL,16,Fwould slash benefits for about 800,000
OL,17,Fpeople.
